      "span_text": "A gallic acid standard curve was obtained for the calculation of polyphenolic content which amounted to 55% as determined spectrophotometrically at 765 nm (LAMBDA 25 UV spectrophotometer, Perkin Elmer, UK) [CITATION_1] ."
